It pays to know the person coming after you,finch.

157
00:09:45,885 --> 00:09:47,735
他们现在要离开了
Okay,they're leaving now.

158
00:09:47,765 --> 00:09:48,775
你最好快点
You'd better hurry up.

159
00:09:48,825 --> 00:09:52,255
- 快好了 - 算了 快走
- Almost got it. - Forget it.Get out of there now.

160
00:09:58,365 --> 00:10:00,315
我们有图像了吗?
Do we have picture?

161
00:10:01,175 --> 00:10:02,905
***

162
00:10:02,905 --> 00:10:05,705
还有一个GPS跟踪器 做得好 Harold
And a gps tracker. Nice work,harold.

163
00:10:05,755 --> 00:10:09,975
我们得全天候看着她 即使她在警局也不例外
We need eyes and ears on her 24-7,even inside the precinct.

164
00:10:17,175 --> 00:10:20,295
Finch Carter走向Hector的铺子里去了
Finch,carter's going right into hector's shop.

165
00:10:20,335 --> 00:10:23,975
Ronnie Middleton枪杀案的首要嫌疑人
Primary suspect in the ronnie middleton shooting.

166
00:10:24,535 --> 00:10:27,395
生意怎么样 Hector?
How's the car business,hector?

167
00:10:29,355 --> 00:10:31,665
说的好像你真的关心似的 警探 
You say that like you really care,detective.

168
00:10:31,695 --> 00:10:33,785
我关心你昨晚在哪里
Care about where you were last night.

169
00:10:33,825 --> 00:10:36,145
来吧 随便扯淡 来忽悠我吧
Go ahead,spin that yarn,dazzle me.

170
00:10:36,185 --> 00:10:38,965
抱歉 我可是恋家的男人
Sorry. I'm a domesticated man.

171
00:10:38,985 --> 00:10:43,125
我在家和我女人一起 看电视 问她
I was back with my old lady,watching some show.Ask her.

172
00:10:43,295 --> 00:10:47,125
当然了 总是这种忠贞的不在场证明
Of course. Always with the loyal alibi.

173
00:10:47,935 --> 00:10:50,505
你知道吗 Monica 他是挺帅 可你能找到更好的
You know,monica,he's handsome,but you can do better.

174
00:10:50,535 --> 00:10:52,995
你敢一个人来这还真是有种 女士
you got some huevos coming down here all alone,lady.

175
00:10:53,045 --> 00:10:56,785
那么说 昨晚在华盛顿高地 出现的不是你的肌肉车?
So that wasn't your muscle car took a detour into washington heights last night?

176
00:10:56,835 --> 00:10:59,555
不 我听说那里很危险的
Nah,I hear it's dangerous down there.

177
00:11:00,305 --> 00:11:03,075
我知道 你们都听说Ronnie Middleton的事了
I know y'all heard what happened to ronnie middleton.

178
00:11:03,115 --> 00:11:05,635
我听说他吃了颗子弹 消化不良
I heard he ate a bullet that didn't agree with him.

179
00:11:07,985 --> 00:11:11,835
不错的铺子 不错的工具
Nice shop,nice tools.

180
00:11:12,145 --> 00:11:14,595
自己活得不错 Hector
Doing well for yourself,hector.

181
00:11:14,615 --> 00:11:17,065
你修修旧车 就赚这么多钱?
You make all this money fixing up old cars?

182
00:11:17,115 --> 00:11:19,525
我有前科 得为自己干活
I got a record. I got to work for myself.

183
00:11:19,545 --> 00:11:21,905
这辆车不错 介意我看看吗?
This is a nice ride. You mind if I check it out?

184
00:11:21,975 --> 00:11:23,575
当然介意了
Sure as hell do.

185
00:11:23,605 --> 00:11:25,705
要看就拿搜查令来
You're gonna need a warrant for that.

186
00:11:28,925 --> 00:11:31,235
你搞砸了 杀了那孩子 Hector
You messed up,taking that kid out,hector.

187
00:11:31,255 --> 00:11:33,405
那孩子的事 我感到很惋惜...
It's a shame what happened to that kid...

188
00:11:33,465 --> 00:11:35,505
即使他就是一告密小混混
Even if he was a punk-ass snitch.

189
00:11:35,545 --> 00:11:38,035
这次你不会再逃脱了
You won't get away with it again.

190
00:11:38,295 --> 00:11:41,725
我会找到办法定你罪
I will find a way to bring you down.

191
00:11:42,565 --> 00:11:45,645
祝你有好运能拿到搜查令 警探
Good luck with that warrant,detective.

192
00:11:55,215 --> 00:11:58,275
不知道你还收集娃娃啊 finch
Didn't know you collected dolls,finch.

193
00:11:59,185 --> 00:12:02,365
你知道的 我收集绝版书 Reese先生
As you know,I collect rare books,Mr.Reese.

194
00:12:02,435 --> 00:12:08,515
还有 180克黑胶唱片 施乐Alto电脑 如果我能找到的话
180-gram vinyl and a xerox alto when I can find one.

195
00:12:09,505 --> 00:12:12,095
娃娃是给Fusco警探的
This doll is for detective fusco.

196
00:12:12,155 --> 00:12:13,985
Fusco喜欢娃娃?
Fusco's into dolls?

197
00:12:14,015 --> 00:12:17,325
如果我们想监视Carter警探的话 他现在就得开始喜欢了
He is now,if we want to keep eyes on detective carter.

198
00:12:17,365 --> 00:12:20,035
我保证会送到他桌子上
I'll make sure it lands on his desk.

199
00:12:20,415 --> 00:12:22,965
我详查了一下咱们的号码
I've been looking into our new number.

200
00:12:23,835 --> 00:12:27,345
<i>纽约警局任职记录</i>
******

201
00:12:23,745 --> 00:12:27,495
Carter 凶杀专案组一级警探
Carter,detective first grade,homicide task force.

202
00:12:27,545 --> 00:12:32,105
单身母亲 一个十几岁的儿子 过去在部队里专门审讯犯人
Single mom,teenage son,served as an army interrogator.

203
00:12:32,145 --> 00:12:35,015
2004年通过律师考试 但放弃做律师 回到军队
Passed the bar in '04,gave it up to go back on the force.

204
00:12:35,045 --> 00:12:36,515
了不起啊 Reese先生
It's impressive,Mr.Reese.

205
00:12:36,545 --> 00:12:38,825
了不起的女士 诚实得有点过分
Impressive lady.Honest to a fault.

206
00:12:38,875 --> 00:12:43,765
那意味着 黑白两道她都得罪了很多人
Which means she made a lot of enemies,both in the criminal world and in her own department.

207
00:12:43,775 --> 00:12:49,015
我把可能的嫌犯名单 缩小到了300个人左右
I've narrowed the list of possible suspects to a little over 300 or so.

208
00:12:49,025 --> 00:12:51,265
凶杀案警探生活中普通的一天
Day in the life of a homicide detective.

209
00:12:51,275 --> 00:12:53,885
有什么更紧迫的威胁吗?
Any more immediate threats?

210
00:12:55,525 --> 00:13:01,695
Hector Alvarez... 是她6个月前的办的一个案子的嫌犯
Hector alvarez... Indicted for homicide on a case she worked six months ago...

211
00:13:01,705 --> 00:13:03,145
但是控罪都撤销了
Till the charges were dropped.

212
00:13:03,165 --> 00:13:06,545
Edward kovach 多次累犯 虐待妻子
Edward kovach - Repeat felon,spouse abuser,

213
00:13:06,575 --> 00:13:10,165
她非常想保护他的妻子 然后就是 Elias
whose wife she's taken a keen interest in protecting.And then there's elias-

214
00:13:10,205 --> 00:13:14,475
残忍的杀手 黑帮头子 已经试过杀她了
Ruthless killer,organized crime boss,who's already taken a shot at her.

215
00:13:14,495 --> 00:13:18,125
她就是一活动靶子 一刻也不能让她离开视线
Well,she's a walking target.Gonna have to keep her in sight at all times.

216
00:13:18,175 --> 00:13:21,205
你得小心点 太接近会有被抓的危险
You have to be careful.Get too close,you risk getting caught.

217
00:13:21,245 --> 00:13:23,275
这个险我得冒
That's a chance I got to take.

218
00:13:23,285 --> 00:13:25,605
不然我要怎么做 就由她吃枪子?
What am I supposed to do,let her catch a bullet?

219
00:13:25,625 --> 00:13:27,165
要是她捉着你怎么办?
What will you do if she catches you?

220
00:13:27,195 --> 00:13:30,805
我相信你会想办法的 Harold
Well,I'm sure you'll figure something out,harold.

221
00:13:36,025 --> 00:13:37,665
*****

222
00:13:44,955 --> 00:13:46,735
搞什么鬼?
What the hell?

223
00:13:52,225 --> 00:13:53,695
Fusco警探
Detective fusco.

224
00:13:53,725 --> 00:13:55,975
生日快乐 Lionel
Happy birthday,lionel.

225
00:13:56,565 --> 00:13:58,055
谢谢 不用了
Thanks,but no thanks.

226
00:13:58,085 --> 00:14:00,595
今天不是我生日 我不知道你到底目的何在
It's not my birthday.I don't know what the hell you're trying to tell me here.

227
00:14:00,625 --> 00:14:03,245
你只要放在桌子上对着Carter就行了
Just put it on your desk and face it towards carter.

228
00:14:03,275 --> 00:14:04,535
为什么?
Why?

229
00:14:04,585 --> 00:14:09,025
因为里面装了摄像头 我们需要知道她都跟谁谈了话
'Cause there's a camera inside,and we need to know everyone she's talking to.

230
00:14:11,155 --> 00:14:13,415
你知道我不知道的事?
You know something I don't?

231
00:14:13,695 --> 00:14:15,785
- 她有麻烦了? - 你说呢
- She in trouble? - Well,you tell me.

232
00:14:15,825 --> 00:14:19,285
跟你局里的黑警同胞们打听一下
Ask around with some of your corrupt pals inside the force.

233
00:14:19,315 --> 00:14:21,305
嘿 怎么了? 你想要什么?
Hey,what's going on? What do you need?

234
00:14:21,335 --> 00:14:23,905
我要查出是谁想要杀Carter
I need to find out who might want to take carter out.

235
00:14:23,935 --> 00:14:26,145
哇哦 等等 我可不能扯进这种事里去
Whoa,wait a minute.I can't be involved in something like that.

236
00:14:26,165 --> 00:14:29,975
不 Lionel 快把摄像头朝向她
No,lionel,just turn the camera towards her desk.

237
00:14:33,525 --> 00:14:35,245
不错的娃娃
Nice doll.

238
00:14:35,445 --> 00:14:38,155
嗯 我的 我的儿子送我的
Yeah,my,uh - My son gave it to me.

239
00:14:39,145 --> 00:14:40,845
监狱里的老先生怎么了?
How'd it go with the old don at the big house?

240
00:14:40,855 --> 00:14:45,165
想探探他 看他对自己的亲生儿子了解多少
Tried to reach out,see what he knew about his biological son.

241
00:14:45,205 --> 00:14:48,115
- Elias哈? - 老头不睬我
Elias,huh? Old man just shut me down.

242
00:14:48,145 --> 00:14:51,075
似乎是觉得所有警察都是坏的
Seems to think every cop is dirty.

243
00:14:51,485 --> 00:14:55,055
嗯 也许他那会是这样子
Yeah. Maybe back in his day.

244
00:14:55,065 --> 00:14:57,485
那个杂货店店主Castillo来了吗?
That bodega owner castillo come in yet?

245
00:14:57,535 --> 00:14:59,345
据我所知没有
Not that I know of.

246
00:14:59,605 --> 00:15:01,855
看来得再去找他
Gonna have to pay him another visit.

247
00:15:02,185 --> 00:15:03,555
一起吗?
You coming?

248
00:15:03,595 --> 00:15:05,335
不 要不 你自己去?
Nah,you know what?Why don't you,uh,go ahead?

249
00:15:05,375 --> 00:15:08,095
我 我有点事 一会去找你 好吗?
I - I got a thing.I'll catch up with you later,okay?

250
00:15:08,135 --> 00:15:09,545
好
Okay.

251
00:15:24,575 --> 00:15:25,985
- 过来 - 嘿 我啥都没做
- Come here. - Yo,I ain't done nothing.

252
00:15:26,015 --> 00:15:27,455
- 手放在我看得见的地方 - 放开
- Hands where I can see 'em. - Get off.

253
00:15:27,515 --> 00:15:30,235
有针头吗? 有会刺伤我的东西吗?
Got any needles? Anything that's gonna stick me?

254
00:15:30,235 --> 00:15:32,155
这是侵犯我的公民权利
This is violation of my civil liberties.

255
00:15:32,175 --> 00:15:34,445
Finch 事情要不妙
Finch,I don't like the looks of this.

256
00:15:35,315 --> 00:15:36,935
婊子 你最好放开我
Bitch,you better get your hands off me.

257
00:15:36,965 --> 00:15:38,995
闭嘴 头低下
Shut up and get your head down.

258
00:15:40,305 --> 00:15:43,725
感谢你把它搞得跟真的似的 警探
Yo,thanks for making it look good,detective.

259
00:15:43,765 --> 00:15:45,085
我想我把手腕给拧了
I think I tweaked my wrist,man.

260
00:15:45,115 --> 00:15:47,525
刚才有点太戏剧化了 
That was a little too theatrical,bottlecap.

261
00:15:47,555 --> 00:15:49,015
- 嘿 - 等等 Reese
- Hey- - Wait a minute,reese.

262
00:15:49,045 --> 00:15:50,645
我想她认识他
I think she knows him.

263
00:15:51,045 --> 00:15:53,895
刚才都是演戏 他一定是她的线人
It's all for show.Must be one of her c.i.s.

264
00:15:53,915 --> 00:15:58,365
那是因为上次我被抓以后 我就花时间戒毒了
That's 'cause after I last got popped,I used my time to rehabilitate myself.

265
00:15:58,385 --> 00:16:00,065
你戒毒了?
You got clean?

266
00:16:00,095 --> 00:16:03,795
- 得了吧 B.C. - 我认真的 我身体里一点毒都没了
- Come on now,b.c. - I'm serious. These pipes are junk-free.

267
00:16:03,855 --> 00:16:07,155
但我还是缺点钱 懂我意思吗?
But I can always use some scratch,you know what I'm saying?

268
00:16:07,175 --> 00:16:10,985
我想知道关于一个 叫Elias的新人你都听到些什么
I need to know what you've heard about the new guy elias.

269
00:16:12,055 --> 00:16:16,075
嗯 最近经常听到这名字
Yeah,I've been hearing that name up and coming a lot.

270
00:16:16,135 --> 00:16:21,625
我没见过他 不过我听说 此人可不是闹着玩的
I never seen him,but I-I hear he's a man not to be trifled with.

271
00:16:21,675 --> 00:16:26,295
昨晚168街和奥杜邦交界的枪杀案 听到些什么消息吗?
You,um,know anything about that shooting last night over on 168th and audubon?

272
00:16:26,325 --> 00:16:28,155
驾车枪击 对吧?
Drive-by,right?

273
00:16:28,175 --> 00:16:30,295
我知道那地方 但不知道谁干的
I know the block,just not the players.

274
00:16:30,315 --> 00:16:35,445
你听过个叫Hector Alvarez的人吗 看到过他开着肌肉车在街区里晃吗?
You ever hear the name hector alvarez come up or see him cruise the block in his g.t.o.?

275
00:16:36,015 --> 00:16:42,025
我没见过那车 也没听有人 谈起Hector 但我会去打听
I didn't see the car or hear nobody talk about hector,but I can ask around.

276
00:16:42,185 --> 00:16:44,205
留神点 B.C.
Good looking out,b.c.

277
00:16:44,335 --> 00:16:49,685
如果你有Hector或者Elias的消息 还会有更多钱
If you get anything back on,um,hector or elias,there's more where that came from.

278
00:16:59,095 --> 00:17:00,575
嘿 队长
Hey,captain.

279
00:17:00,595 --> 00:17:02,625
欢迎回来 警探
Welcome back,detective.

280
00:17:02,645 --> 00:17:04,605
没想到你跟市区那些
Didn't think you'd grace us with your presence again

281
00:17:04,625 --> 00:17:09,025
喷香水的人一起后还会赏脸回来
once you spent time with the perfumed folk downtown.

282
00:17:09,295 --> 00:17:11,105
你这个笨蛋是怎么发达的?
How'd a half-wit like you pull that off?

283
00:17:11,145 --> 00:17:14,085
我想我这笨蛋还是有一手的 嗯 队长?
I guess the half-wit's still got some juice,huh,captain?

284
00:17:14,935 --> 00:17:18,025
他们让我和Carter警探搭档...
They got me working with detective carter,and...

285
00:17:18,775 --> 00:17:20,215
我听到些传言
I'm starting to hear some things.

286
00:17:20,235 --> 00:17:22,875
是嘛? 比如?
Yeah? Like what?

287
00:17:22,895 --> 00:17:27,555
也许 呃 有些人不喜欢她
Maybe she's not so well-liked by,uh,a certain element.

288
00:17:28,695 --> 00:17:32,195
听着 Lionel... 事情又恢复往昔了
Listen,lionel... Things are going back to the way they used to be.

289
00:17:32,215 --> 00:17:35,215
- 往昔? - 黑帮那些事儿?
- Used to be? - Thing about organized crime?

290
00:17:35,295 --> 00:17:37,905
有组织 管用
It was organized.Things worked.

291
00:17:37,935 --> 00:17:39,325
一切守时有序
Trains ran on time.

292
00:17:39,365 --> 00:17:43,805
这个新人... 他懂规矩
This new guy... He knows the rules.

293
00:17:43,835 --> 00:17:46,775
新人 你是说Elias
New guy - You mean elias.

294
00:17:46,815 --> 00:17:50,025
组织管理得很严密... 低调
Runs a tight ship... Low profile.

295
00:17:50,025 --> 00:17:52,345
跟那些凶残的俄国白痴不一样
Not like these cutthroat russian idiots.

296
00:17:52,365 --> 00:17:56,565
他知道要贿赂谁... 关节一直通到市政府里
He knows who to grease... All the way up to city hall.

297
00:17:56,585 --> 00:17:58,405
听着 现在的经济情况就是一坨屎
Look,the economy's in the toilet.

298
00:17:58,445 --> 00:18:01,555
Carter警探不懂游戏规则
Detective carter doesn't understand the rules.

299
00:18:01,595 --> 00:18:04,195
她对生意不好
She's bad for business.

300
00:18:04,725 --> 00:18:05,605
她做了什么?
What'd she do?

301
00:18:05,625 --> 00:18:08,495
到处查探... 想要找证据
Sniffing around... Trying to build a case.

302
00:18:08,545 --> 00:18:12,395
她枪头直指Elias 必须解决她
She's gunning for elias.She's got to go.

303
00:18:13,405 --> 00:18:15,295
杀一个警察可不容易
It's a tricky business,getting rid of a cop.

304
00:18:15,325 --> 00:18:20,395
通过合适的后门...  直接通过上面下命令 
Went through the proper back channels... Up the chain of command.

305
00:18:20,775 --> 00:18:22,315
已经授权了
Permission granted.

306
00:18:22,345 --> 00:18:25,465
只需要做得... 干净
It's just got to look... Clean.

307
00:18:25,495 --> 00:18:29,965
"干净"?  你是说弄得像殉职?
"Clean"? You mean like in the line of duty?

308
00:18:31,745 --> 00:18:34,585
我开始觉得被夹在中间啊
I'm starting to feel caught in the middle here,captain.

309
00:18:35,575 --> 00:18:38,025
如果我是你 就保持距离
I'd keep my distance,if I were you.

310
00:18:48,825 --> 00:18:52,395
你没有去警局啊 你答应我的 Castillo先生
You didn't come down to the precinct like you told me you would,mr.Castillo.

311
00:18:52,405 --> 00:18:55,135
今天我没帮手 我很忙
I got no help today. I'm a very busy man.

312
00:18:55,185 --> 00:18:58,545
枪击发生前后 你有没有见过这辆车?
