But don't expect me and my men to back you up.

653
00:40:06,081 --> 00:40:08,421
战事漫长
It's a long war.

654
00:40:08,551 --> 00:40:10,521
只你孤身一人
And you're all alone.

655
00:40:19,041 --> 00:40:22,431
幸好你接受我的建议穿了防弹衣
Glad you took my advice about wearing that vest,detective.

656
00:40:22,591 --> 00:40:24,781
我知道这改变不了什么
I know this doesn't change anything.

657
00:40:25,381 --> 00:40:27,901
我知道一有机会你还会逮捕我
I know you'll still arrest me if you get the chance.

658
00:40:27,911 --> 00:40:32,501
