Unlike your pal elias.

667
00:41:10,001 --> 00:41:13,551
我不认识你 但你在威胁一个警队队长
I don't know who you are,but you're threatening a captain.

668
00:41:13,831 --> 00:41:15,881
好吧 好吧
Okay,okay,okay.

669
00:41:15,951 --> 00:41:18,731
Elias没有批准不会杀警察
Elias can't kill a cop without permission.

670
00:41:18,801 --> 00:41:21,051
传话给指挥链
Run this up the chain of command.

671
00:41:21,241 --> 00:41:23,711
