- You got that? - Yeah.

675
00:41:52,001 --> 00:41:54,921
外婆说你又过了规定时间才回家
Grandma said you were late for curfew again.

676
00:41:54,961 --> 00:41:57,791
拜托 妈 你来真的?
Oh,come on,ma.You're serious?

677
00:41:57,821 --> 00:42:00,091
我去参加舞会了
I was at a dance.

678
00:42:00,151 --> 00:42:02,021
她漂亮不?
Is she pretty?

679
00:42:04,471 --> 00:42:06,551
最好还得聪明
Better be smart too.

680
00:42:06,581 --> 00:42:08,791
又聪明又漂亮
Smart and pretty.

681
00:42:15,251 --> 00:42:18,721
