Wouldn't know how to if I tried.

686
00:42:36,051 --> 00:42:39,281
我不喜欢 你每天在外面
I don't like it - You out there every day.

687
00:42:39,401 --> 00:42:41,071
谁能保护你呢?
Who's got your back?

688
00:42:43,671 --> 00:42:45,911
你不用担心我
You don't have to worry about me.

689
